criteria.textblock:
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  >50 years of age;

          -  At least one untreated T1a tumour of one kidney (tumour ≤ 4 cm in greatest dimension);

          -  Signed IRB-approved informed consent form.

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Pregnancy or breast feeding;

          -  Known hypersensitivity or HACA against Girentuximab.

          -  Administration of experimental medication for imaging purposes within three months
             before administration of Indium-111-Girentuximab for this study, except the
             administration of Girentuximab labeled with a random isotope.
